Instructs node set to destroy nodes parent doc when node set is destroyed.</para>
<para>

</para><informaltable pgwide="1" frame="none" role="params">
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colwidth="2*">
<colspec colwidth="8*">
<tbody>
<row><entry align="right"><parameter>nset</parameter>&nbsp;:</entry>
